name: Corneo's Ranni (Elden Ring) TI Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for Ranni the Witch from Elden Ring.

This was a fun challenge, and perhaps no surprise that SD doesn't really want to generate images with 4 arms. I'm still not sure if it helps but I think you should include extra_arms on your prompts using this (assuming you want to go for 4-armed accuracy). Also one_eye_closed if you're a real purist. cracked_skin and doll_joints should either go in the positive or negative prompt depending on if you want lore-accurate doll-body Ranni or a smooth human body.

Be warned that despite some SFW gens here, this embedding is extremely NSFW-happy and will often give you a mostly nude Ranni unprompted.

Example images created using my 7th Heaven mix https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
